description:
The W3C Board Finance Committee assists the Board in fulfilling its oversight responsibilities to hold the Consortium to account regarding:
<ul>
    <li>On-going financial viability;
    <li>Financial budgets and the availability of all analysis relevant to Consortium finances;
    <li>Internal controls and financial/accounting processes;
    <li>Accuracy and timeliness of financial statements.
</ul>
Learn more in its <a href="https://www.w3.org/2022/10/bod-finance.html">2022 charter</a>.
